msgid "邮件协议族"
msgstr "Email Protocol Suite"

#: ../../source/network/mail.rst:5
msgid "简介"
msgstr "Introduction"

#: ../../source/network/mail.rst:8
msgid "SMTP"
msgstr "SMTP"

#: ../../source/network/mail.rst:9
msgid ""
"SMTP (Simple Mail Transfer Protocol) "
"是一种电子邮件传输的协议，是一组用于从源地址到目的地址传输邮件的规范。不启用SSL时端口号为25，启用SSL时端口号多为465或994。"
msgstr "SMTP (Simple Mail Transfer Protocol) is an email transfer protocol, a set of specifications for sending mail from a source address to a destination address. When SSL is not enabled, it uses port 25; when SSL is enabled, it commonly uses port 465 or 994."

#: ../../source/network/mail.rst:12
msgid "POP3"
msgstr "POP3"

#: ../../source/network/mail.rst:13
msgid ""
"POP3 (Post Office Protocol 3) "
"用于支持使用客户端远程管理在服务器上的电子邮件。不启用SSL时端口号为110，启用SSL时端口号多为995。"
msgstr "POP3 (Post Office Protocol 3) supports remote management of email stored on a server from a client. When SSL is not enabled, it uses port 110; when SSL is enabled, it commonly uses port 995."

#: ../../source/network/mail.rst:16
msgid "IMAP"
msgstr "IMAP"

#: ../../source/network/mail.rst:17
msgid ""
"IMAP (Internet Mail Access "
"Protocol)，即交互式邮件存取协议，它是跟POP3类似邮件访问标准协议之一。不同的是，开启了IMAP后，您在电子邮件客户端收取的邮件仍然保留在服务器上，同时在客户端上的操作都会反馈到服务器上，如：删除邮件，标记已读等，服务器上的邮件也会做相应的动作。不启用SSL时端口号为143，启用SSL时端口号多为993。"
msgstr "IMAP (Internet Mail Access Protocol) is a standard mail access protocol similar to POP3. The difference is that after IMAP is enabled, messages retrieved by an email client remain on the server, and client-side actions such as deleting messages or marking them as read are synchronized back to the server. When SSL is not enabled, it uses port 143; when SSL is enabled, it commonly uses port 993."

#: ../../source/network/mail.rst:20
msgid "防护策略"
msgstr "Protection Strategies"

#: ../../source/network/mail.rst:23
msgid "SPF"
msgstr "SPF"

#: ../../source/network/mail.rst:24
msgid ""
"发件人策略框架 (Sender Policy Framework, SPF) "
"是一套电子邮件认证机制，用于确认电子邮件是否由网域授权的邮件服务器寄出，防止有人伪冒身份网络钓鱼或寄出垃圾邮件。SPF允许管理员设定一个DNS "
"TXT记录或SPF记录设定发送邮件服务器的IP范围，如有任何邮件并非从上述指明授权的IP地址寄出，则很可能该邮件并非确实由真正的寄件者寄出。"
msgstr "Sender Policy Framework (SPF) is an email authentication mechanism used to confirm whether an email was sent by a mail server authorized by the domain, helping prevent phishing and spam sent under a forged identity. SPF allows administrators to configure a DNS TXT record or SPF record that defines the IP ranges of authorized sending mail servers. If a message is not sent from one of those authorized IP addresses, it is likely not truly from the claimed sender."

#: ../../source/network/mail.rst:27
msgid "DKIM"
msgstr "DKIM"

#: ../../source/network/mail.rst:28
msgid ""
"域名密钥识别邮件 (DomainKeys Identified Mail, DKIM) 是一种检测电子邮件发件人地址伪造的方法"
"。发送方会在邮件的头中插入DKIM-Signature，收件方通过查询DNS记录中的公钥来验证发件人的信息。"
msgstr "DomainKeys Identified Mail (DKIM) is a method for detecting forged email sender addresses. The sender inserts a DKIM-Signature into the message header, and the recipient verifies the sender information by querying the public key in DNS records."

#: ../../source/network/mail.rst:31
msgid "DMARC"
msgstr "DMARC"

#: ../../source/network/mail.rst:32
msgid ""
"基于网域的消息认证、报告和一致性 (Domain-based Message Authentication, Reporting and "
"Conformance, DMARC) 是电子邮件身份验证协议，用于解决在邮件栏中显示的域名和验证的域名不一致的问题。要通过 DMARC "
"检查，必须通过 SPF 或/和 DKIM 的身份验证，且需要标头地址中的域名必须与经过身份验证的域名一致。"
msgstr "Domain-based Message Authentication, Reporting, and Conformance (DMARC) is an email authentication protocol used to address mismatches between the domain displayed in the message header and the authenticated domain. To pass a DMARC check, a message must pass SPF and/or DKIM authentication, and the domain in the header address must align with the authenticated domain."

